476
00:47:59,860 --> 00:48:03,480
<i>There's no need to be nervous,</i> <i>Dr. Leavitt.</i>

477
00:48:04,310 --> 00:48:08,270
<i>Please raise your left arm.</i>

478
00:48:15,420 --> 00:48:19,610
<i>Please sit up,</i> <i>facing the scan screen</i> <i>and watch carefully.</i>

479
00:48:42,010 --> 00:48:46,070
<i>You have received</i> <i>pneumatic injections</i> <i>of booster immunizations.</i>

480
00:48:46,140 --> 00:48:48,400
<i>You may get dressed.</i> <i>Thank you.</i>

481
00:48:48,470 --> 00:48:50,990
<i>This recording is now ended.</i>

482
00:48:56,890 --> 00:49:00,430
