00:58:25,050 --> 00:58:29,140
<i>Negative "N" scan.</i> <i>Negative "N" scope in LY-1.</i>

599
00:58:29,210 --> 00:58:33,270
<i>Affirmative.</i> <i>"N" indicator in MP-4.</i> <i>I will repeat.</i>

600
00:58:33,340 --> 00:58:37,650
<i>Negative "N" scan.</i> <i>Negative "N" scope in LY-1.</i>

601
00:58:37,720 --> 00:58:41,360
<i>Affirmative.</i> <i>"N indicator in MP-4.</i>

